# v0.55 — Web Save Sync (IndexedDB)

### New Files
- `scripts/gamestate.gd` — Enhanced GameState autoload
  - Detects web platform automatically (`OS.has_feature("web")`)
  - Saves to `localStorage` via `JavaScriptBridge` when on web
  - Falls back to `user://` file on native builds
  - Auto-syncs every 30 seconds during gameplay
  - Syncs on scene changes and game pause

### Updated
- `project.godot` — GameState autoload persists across scenes
- All chapter scenes call `GameState.save_game()` on completion

